         <notesStmt>
            <note type="summary">1. Thanks for Rovigo's assistance. 2. Benjamin ha-Kohen
                            has promised that he will send to Rovigo the replies he received from
                            Zacuto concerning "secrets" and kawwanot.Kohen also had Neḥemias copy
                            yiḥudim for tiqqun shovevim who also worked on the copy of Sefer
                            ha-Kawwanot for Rovigo. Z. will see to it that the copies of Sefer
                            ha-Kinuyyim and novella on Yodʿei Binah will be sent to Rovigo. He paid
                            almost one Hungarian ducat for the two volumes more than Rovigo had
                            sent. David Aviaṭar expects payments of another ducat for his work.
                            Payment of these debts leaves in Z's hands six pounds and 6 scudi. 3. Z.
                            thanks for the wine Rovigo sent him.</note>
            <note type="incipit" xml:lang="he">את קולך שמעתי</note>
